WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.030
Hey, good morning family. How are

00:00:03.030 --> 00:00:03.040
you all

00:00:03.040 --> 00:00:05.110
doing today? I’m going to talk to

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:08.230
you about the angelic visitations

00:00:08.230 --> 00:00:08.240
I’ve

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:10.470
had.

00:00:10.470 --> 00:00:10.480
I’ve

00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:13.509
had several angelic visitations over the years and

00:00:13.519 --> 00:00:16.150
the Lord has been amazing;

00:00:16.150 --> 00:00:16.160
I’ve

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:19.550
seen some really cool stuff.

00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:23.029
This time, we were just

00:00:23.039 --> 00:00:25.189
praying. It was a normal night

00:00:25.199 --> 00:00:27.910
in the same house

00:00:27.910 --> 00:00:27.920
and

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:29.750
everything was the same.

00:00:29.760 --> 00:00:32.709
We were praying and went

00:00:32.719 --> 00:00:36.069
to bed, and all of a sudden my wife and I

00:00:36.079 --> 00:00:36.870
were

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:39.590
woken up out of our sleep. It

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:42.709
was early in the morning and

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:46.950
the whole house shook. It sounded like

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:49.270
the whole roof was going to

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:52.709
come off our house and my wife said,

00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:54.549
'Oh, did you hear that?'She woke me

00:00:54.559 --> 00:00:56.310
and I said, 'Yes, I heard it. It woke me

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:58.549
up, too. I think

00:00:58.549 --> 00:00:58.559
somebody’s

00:00:58.559 --> 00:00:59.670
trying to break into our

00:00:59.670 --> 00:00:59.680
house,'and

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:02.389
I said, 'Let me go

00:01:02.389 --> 00:01:02.399
check.'I

00:01:02.399 --> 00:01:05.030
grabbed my pistol and went

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:06.630
to

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:08.390
check our home to make sure that

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:12.230
nobody was

00:01:12.230 --> 00:01:12.240
there.

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:15.190
All of a sudden, I looked out

00:01:15.190 --> 00:01:15.200
while

00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:17.749
standing by the door. I

00:01:17.749 --> 00:01:17.759
stood

00:01:17.759 --> 00:01:20.710
up and my eyes were

00:01:20.710 --> 00:01:20.720
opened

00:01:20.720 --> 00:01:25.550
to the spirit realm.

00:01:25.550 --> 00:01:25.560
I

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:27.510
saw

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:31.469
four demons. They were four demonic

00:01:31.479 --> 00:01:35.190
spirits covered with scales,

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:35.950
with

00:01:35.960 --> 00:01:39.429
nasty-looking

00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:42.789
hair growing out of them and

00:01:42.799 --> 00:01:46.149
warts. Their eyes were

00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:49.069
slanted and red.

00:01:49.079 --> 00:01:52.149
One had

00:01:52.149 --> 00:01:52.159
a pig-looking

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:54.870
nose with tusks coming up. The other

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:58.709
was completely black;

00:01:58.719 --> 00:02:01.030
there was no shape to it. It looked kind

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:04.310
of like

00:02:04.320 --> 00:02:06.950
a ghost, but it was just a black,

00:02:06.950 --> 00:02:06.960
misty-looking

00:02:06.960 --> 00:02:09.589
thing. The

00:02:09.589 --> 00:02:09.599
others were

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:10.949
different shapes.

00:02:10.949 --> 00:02:10.959
I’m

00:02:10.959 --> 00:02:11.910
not going to give

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:14.309
any more glory to it, but every single

00:02:14.319 --> 00:02:15.750
one of them was there,

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:19.110
trying to get into the house.

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:21.350
They shook the roof

00:02:21.350 --> 00:02:21.360
of

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:24.710
the house in the natural, and like

00:02:24.720 --> 00:02:26.630
I said, it startled both of us and woke

00:02:26.640 --> 00:02:29.150
us up, but they couldn't get

00:02:29.160 --> 00:02:31.910
in. The Lord didn't show me this at the

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:35.509
time, but I saw them grunting and hissing,

00:02:35.519 --> 00:02:38.550
carrying on while

00:02:38.550 --> 00:02:38.560
passing

00:02:38.560 --> 00:02:41.350
by on the street. I didn't

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:43.190
understand why they couldn't come past.

00:02:43.200 --> 00:02:45.949
All of a sudden, I

00:02:45.959 --> 00:02:48.750
saw massive,

00:02:48.760 --> 00:02:52.550
humongous angels chained

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:54.710
together. Their arms were

00:02:54.710 --> 00:02:54.720
linked

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:57.030
together, like

00:02:57.030 --> 00:02:57.040
when

00:02:57.040 --> 00:02:59.110
you cross your arms with

00:03:01.030 --> 00:03:01.040
someone

00:03:03.159 --> 00:03:06.030
else;

00:03:10.350 --> 00:03:10.360
that’s

00:03:12.360 --> 00:03:17.270
how they

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:20.390
were standing.

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:29.750
They were standing strong, and the

00:03:29.750 --> 00:03:29.760
demonic spirits

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:32.869
were hitting against those angelic

00:03:32.879 --> 00:03:35.509
beings,

00:03:35.509 --> 00:03:35.519
but

00:03:35.519 --> 00:03:37.990
they couldn't get past them. Every

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:40.229
night before we go to bed, we put

00:03:40.229 --> 00:03:40.239
chain-linked

00:03:40.239 --> 00:03:42.869
angels all around our house

00:03:42.879 --> 00:03:44.789
and commission them. We thank you,

00:03:44.799 --> 00:03:47.190
Lord, that the angels are surrounding

00:03:47.200 --> 00:03:49.990
our house, that no devil in hell can come

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:52.789
across the bloodline

00:03:52.789 --> 00:03:52.799
or

00:03:52.799 --> 00:03:55.190
the angels. The angels are

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:56.910
protecting us as we

00:03:56.920 --> 00:04:01.350
sleep, just like we prayed.

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:08.949
It took me

00:04:08.949 --> 00:04:08.959
aback

00:04:08.959 --> 00:04:12.470
so much that I yelled when I saw

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:17.909
this, 'Praise God! Wow! Praise the

00:04:17.909 --> 00:04:17.919
Lord!'I

00:04:17.919 --> 00:04:21.189
saw the angels

00:04:21.199 --> 00:04:23.990
protecting us, and whenever they heard

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:27.310
me praising the Lord, they

00:04:27.320 --> 00:04:30.310
all looked over, turned their

00:04:30.320 --> 00:04:33.510
bodies, and started looking at me,

00:04:33.510 --> 00:04:33.520
saying,

00:04:33.520 --> 00:04:37.350
'Praise the

00:04:37.350 --> 00:04:37.360
Lord!'They

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:40.150
started worshiping the Lord with me.

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:42.230
I turned around and said,

00:04:42.230 --> 00:04:42.240
'Whoa!'because

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:43.909
it took me aback because it

00:04:43.919 --> 00:04:48.550
was so loud. Their voices were so loud

00:04:48.560 --> 00:04:51.350
it sounded like sirens, like

00:04:51.360 --> 00:04:54.710
trumpets, like a blast. 'Praise the Lord!'They

00:04:54.710 --> 00:04:54.720
didn't

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:57.670
say

00:04:57.670 --> 00:04:57.680
it

00:04:57.680 --> 00:05:00.629
individually;

00:05:00.639 --> 00:05:04.030
they said it together. They said,

00:05:04.040 --> 00:05:07.110
'Praise the Lord,'and when they did, it

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:09.270
echoed throughout the area. You

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:10.870
could hear it in the spirit realm; it was

00:05:10.870 --> 00:05:10.880
so loud you

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:12.469
would have

00:05:12.479 --> 00:05:14.270
to hold your ears.

00:05:14.280 --> 00:05:16.629
They started

00:05:16.639 --> 00:05:18.870
praising the Lord with me. Every

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:21.350
time they

00:05:21.350 --> 00:05:21.360
worshiped,

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:24.469
they

00:05:24.479 --> 00:05:27.189
turned to see what I was doing

00:05:27.199 --> 00:05:30.230
and as

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:31.749
I praised the Lord, they started

00:05:31.759 --> 00:05:33.670
praising the Lord too. It became a

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:35.189
chain and we just started praising the

00:05:35.199 --> 00:05:39.189
Lord. At that time, I saw the glory

00:05:39.199 --> 00:05:42.390
coming from the heavens

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:45.510
through a portal,

00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:48.670
and I could see shafts of light coming

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:53.510
through that portal,

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:57.189
making those angels glow. They

00:05:57.199 --> 00:06:00.230
started glowing with a heavenly glory

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:03.350
even brighter as they praised the

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:06.469
Lord. Those shafts of light

00:06:06.469 --> 00:06:06.479
were

00:06:06.479 --> 00:06:08.550
coming out of the

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:10.790
heavens and making them

00:06:15.270 --> 00:06:15.280
stronger—it

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:18.230
was like it was giving them 'super

00:06:18.230 --> 00:06:18.240
juice.'They

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:20.150
were praising

00:06:20.160 --> 00:06:21.590
the Lord with me and getting

00:06:21.600 --> 00:06:24.150
shinier.

00:06:24.160 --> 00:06:26.629
I had completely forgotten about the

00:06:26.639 --> 00:06:28.790
demonic spirits because

00:06:28.800 --> 00:06:30.550
I was caught up in the glory of

00:06:30.560 --> 00:06:33.350
worshiping the angels at the same time.

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:35.590
Every time I said, 'Thank

00:06:35.600 --> 00:06:37.749
you, Jesus,'they would say, 'Thank you,

00:06:39.270 --> 00:06:39.280
Jesus.'This

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:43.350
went on for quite some

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:45.909
time.

00:06:45.919 --> 00:06:48.550
I was taken aback by what I was

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:50.469
seeing in the spirit realm;

00:06:50.479 --> 00:06:52.629
it really was

00:06:52.639 --> 00:06:54.950
amazing. After all this happened, I saw

00:06:54.960 --> 00:06:57.830
the glory come down. It was

00:06:57.830 --> 00:06:57.840
around 4

00:06:57.840 --> 00:06:59.510
or 5 in the morning

00:06:59.520 --> 00:07:01.189
now, and I had

00:07:01.199 --> 00:07:03.189
to go to work the next day by

00:07:03.189 --> 00:07:03.199
eight.

00:07:03.199 --> 00:07:04.950
I went and laid down a little bit

00:07:04.960 --> 00:07:06.550
and dozed off, but it was

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:08.150
hard to

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:11.350
get more rest. I got

00:07:11.360 --> 00:07:15.029
to work the next day at the church

00:07:15.029 --> 00:07:15.039
for

00:07:15.039 --> 00:07:17.990
an all-staff meeting and the

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:20.629
pastor, Pastor Mark, saw

00:07:20.639 --> 00:07:21.909
me sitting in the front.

00:07:21.919 --> 00:07:23.749
I told him, 'I want to tell

00:07:23.759 --> 00:07:25.670
you what happened last night.'He

00:07:25.670 --> 00:07:25.680
said,

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:27.430
'Brandon, I don't doubt it at

00:07:27.440 --> 00:07:29.990
all. As you were talking,

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:31.909
you were shining. I can see

00:07:31.919 --> 00:07:34.230
the glory shining on you.'There

00:07:34.230 --> 00:07:34.240
was

00:07:34.240 --> 00:07:35.830
actually a presence of the Lord

00:07:35.840 --> 00:07:38.629
on me from

00:07:38.639 --> 00:07:40.710
the visitation the night before,

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:48.629
making me shine a little bit.

00:07:48.639 --> 00:07:50.790
Pastor Mark could see

00:07:50.800 --> 00:07:54.150
the glory on me.

00:07:54.150 --> 00:07:54.160
It’s

00:07:54.160 --> 00:07:56.390
just amazing.

00:07:56.390 --> 00:07:56.400
That’s

00:07:56.400 --> 00:07:59.029
how you know I

00:07:59.039 --> 00:08:02.150
live by faith. I

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:04.909
expect angelic visitations and

00:08:04.919 --> 00:08:07.830
manifestations of the glory in my house.

00:08:07.840 --> 00:08:11.029
I expect God to do the impossible and I

00:08:11.039 --> 00:08:13.110
receive it.

00:08:13.120 --> 00:08:14.629
Let me tell you another

00:08:14.639 --> 00:08:16.629
one. There have been times when

00:08:16.629 --> 00:08:16.639
I’ve gone

00:08:16.639 --> 00:08:18.390
through a shady

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:20.309
part of town and felt nervous.

00:08:20.319 --> 00:08:22.550
One time, I

00:08:22.550 --> 00:08:22.560
went

00:08:22.560 --> 00:08:24.710
to the gas station

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:27.670
late at

00:08:27.670 --> 00:08:27.680
night—or

00:08:27.680 --> 00:08:29.350
it

00:08:29.350 --> 00:08:29.360
seemed

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:31.270
late

00:08:31.280 --> 00:08:34.310
because it was winter and the sun goes down so early.

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:38.469
I was nervous to get out

00:08:38.479 --> 00:08:40.870
of the car because of where I was and

00:08:40.870 --> 00:08:40.880
thought,

00:08:40.880 --> 00:08:43.029
'Okay, here we

00:08:43.029 --> 00:08:43.039
go.'I

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:45.430
went out there, and all of a

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:48.710
sudden—because

00:08:48.720 --> 00:08:50.470
God loves you all

00:08:50.470 --> 00:08:50.480
and

00:08:50.480 --> 00:08:52.910
is compassionate—He opened

00:08:52.910 --> 00:08:52.920
my eyes

00:08:52.920 --> 00:08:56.070
for my comfort.

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:58.310
He said, 'Look

00:08:58.320 --> 00:09:00.710
over, son.'I looked to

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:04.350
my left, and there was a

00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:08.070
massive angel standing there

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:11.910
watching over me as I was pumping gas.

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:14.269
The angel was at

00:09:14.279 --> 00:09:18.070
attention. He had muscles upon muscles.

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:20.790
He made Arnold Schwarzenegger look like

00:09:20.800 --> 00:09:23.430
a little weenie, like a little wimpy baby

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:26.230
guy, or even some

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:28.550
big bodybuilder, Mr. Universe. Olympics,

00:09:28.560 --> 00:09:30.230
like some guy that's ripped and

00:09:30.230 --> 00:09:30.240
has

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:32.150
been eating

00:09:32.160 --> 00:09:34.590
nothing but protein, but this

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:38.389
angel had muscle upon muscle and he was

00:09:38.399 --> 00:09:40.710
standing there decked out with this garb

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:42.470
on, it looked like some kind

00:09:42.480 --> 00:09:44.870
of armor, and he was looking out at

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:47.630
attention, watching over

00:09:47.640 --> 00:09:51.190
me. And when I saw that, it took me

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:53.230
back. It took my breath and I went,

00:09:53.230 --> 00:09:53.240
"Whoa."Because

00:09:53.240 --> 00:09:55.829
it's one of

00:09:55.839 --> 00:09:59.110
those things that shows God cares. God cares.

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:02.630
And it blessed me so as

00:10:02.640 --> 00:10:05.590
he was watching out for me. It just

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:08.790
shows that we have angels that keep

00:10:08.800 --> 00:10:10.790
charge over us and they bear us up in

00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:13.829
their hands lest we dash our foot

00:10:13.839 --> 00:10:16.470
against a stone. He promised us in

00:10:16.470 --> 00:10:16.480
Psalm

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:19.030
91 that he would do this. He

00:10:19.040 --> 00:10:20.710
promised us that he would take care of

00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:23.750
us. Do you believe it? Do you believe

00:10:23.760 --> 00:10:26.230
it? That Jesus is still the same

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:28.470
yesterday, today, and forever. And what

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:30.550
he would do for the people in the Bible,

00:10:30.560 --> 00:10:33.829
he'll do for you. He'll protect you. Let

00:10:33.839 --> 00:10:36.630
me tell you another one.

00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:38.670
I was working at the

00:10:38.680 --> 00:10:41.350
church and I told you all about the

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:43.269
healings whenever I'd led prayer and

00:10:43.279 --> 00:10:45.509
the angels bringing in hearts for

00:10:45.519 --> 00:10:47.990
people that needed hearts. For

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:50.509
whatever reason, it was another heart

00:10:50.519 --> 00:10:53.110
testimony and I was just

00:10:53.110 --> 00:10:53.120
vacuuming

00:10:53.120 --> 00:10:55.750
the floor and I'm seeing over in

00:10:55.760 --> 00:10:57.430
this realm of the spirits when this

00:10:57.440 --> 00:11:01.030
happens. But this time the angel

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:04.630
touched me and I literally thought I was

00:11:04.640 --> 00:11:07.190
going to come up out of my skin whenever he

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:10.230
did it because I felt it on my shoulder and

00:11:10.240 --> 00:11:13.750
I was the only one in the room vacuuming

00:11:13.760 --> 00:11:17.190
the church and I went,

00:11:17.190 --> 00:11:17.200
"Whoa."You

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:19.030
get a little startled

00:11:19.030 --> 00:11:19.040
because

00:11:19.040 --> 00:11:21.430
the angel touched me like that and

00:11:21.440 --> 00:11:23.670
I turned around and I'm

00:11:23.680 --> 00:11:25.030
just seeing in the realm of spirit. It's

00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:27.590
not a physical manifestation, nothing

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:29.910
like that; I'm looking in the realm

00:11:29.920 --> 00:11:31.350
of the spirit, but he touched me in the

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:34.550
natural and he said, "I've come to give

00:11:34.560 --> 00:11:36.350
Jim a

00:11:36.350 --> 00:11:36.360
heart."He

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:38.870
goes, "You need to go and tell

00:11:38.880 --> 00:11:40.790
Jim that I've brought him a

00:11:40.790 --> 00:11:40.800
heart."He's

00:11:40.800 --> 00:11:42.470
believing. He's been praying for a

00:11:42.480 --> 00:11:44.230
heart. They're believing for a

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:46.069
miracle because Jim had a bad heart. And

00:11:46.079 --> 00:11:47.990
he was one of the other janitors on

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:51.269
staff. And his blood pressure would drop

00:11:51.279 --> 00:11:53.350
bad, really bad. And he would have to go

00:11:53.360 --> 00:11:55.910
to the ER all the time. And it was very

00:11:55.920 --> 00:11:57.110
serious, some of the stuff that was

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:59.910
happening with his heart.

00:11:59.920 --> 00:12:01.750
So the angel brought this heart and I

00:12:01.760 --> 00:12:03.670
could see in the spirit realm like I'm

00:12:03.680 --> 00:12:05.430
seeing my son right now. I mean

00:12:05.440 --> 00:12:07.829
it was that clear and the angel had a

00:12:07.839 --> 00:12:10.750
heart in his hand just like

00:12:10.750 --> 00:12:10.760
this—and,

00:12:10.760 --> 00:12:13.430
you know what, I take that

00:12:13.430 --> 00:12:13.440
back—it

00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:15.509
was in both hands. He had it in there.

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:16.910
He brought it to

00:12:16.920 --> 00:12:20.150
me and he said, "Go and tell Jim that I

00:12:20.160 --> 00:12:23.670
brought the heart for him."So I said, "Wow,

00:12:23.680 --> 00:12:25.990
okay, what an honor."So I walk

00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:28.389
down the hall and I get all the way down

00:12:28.399 --> 00:12:30.949
the hall and Jim was in room number two because

00:12:30.949 --> 00:12:30.959
the

00:12:30.959 --> 00:12:33.590
rooms weren't labeled at

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:35.670
this church, and he was in room

00:12:35.680 --> 00:12:37.829
two or three and I was cleaning on the

00:12:37.839 --> 00:12:40.629
back side of room 24. Not that that

00:12:40.639 --> 00:12:42.150
matters but I'm just telling you

00:12:42.160 --> 00:12:44.550
for the sake of the story. So I walked

00:12:44.560 --> 00:12:45.750
down the hall and I went in there and

00:12:45.760 --> 00:12:47.829
the angel went in there and I told Jim,

00:12:47.839 --> 00:12:49.990
"Jim, there's an

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:52.470
angel of the Lord here and he has

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:55.110
brought you a heart. Do you

00:12:55.120 --> 00:12:56.550
want to receive it? I'm going to pray for

00:12:56.560 --> 00:12:57.910
you and you're going to receive this

00:12:57.910 --> 00:12:57.920
heart."He

00:12:57.920 --> 00:13:01.389
said, "Man, you ain't seeing

00:13:01.399 --> 00:13:03.910
nothing, dude. Whatever. Like, you're

00:13:03.920 --> 00:13:06.150
crazy. Get out of here, man."He

00:13:06.150 --> 00:13:06.160
was

00:13:06.160 --> 00:13:08.230
totally

00:13:08.230 --> 00:13:08.240
pooh-poohing

00:13:08.240 --> 00:13:10.069
me. Like, "You're a

00:13:10.079 --> 00:13:12.629
weirdo. Get out of here."And I was

00:13:12.639 --> 00:13:14.150
like, "No, really. I really

00:13:14.160 --> 00:13:17.110
see an angelic being. He wants to

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:18.470
bring you a heart. He's brought you a heart.

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:20.069
Do you want the heart?"He goes, "Dude,

00:13:20.079 --> 00:13:21.430
get out of here. Stop bothering me.

00:13:21.440 --> 00:13:22.710
That's

00:13:22.720 --> 00:13:25.030
weird."I

00:13:25.040 --> 00:13:27.590
just looked at him and I went, "Okay,

00:13:27.590 --> 00:13:27.600
fine."I

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:30.310
was offended a little

00:13:30.320 --> 00:13:32.069
bit, like, "Whatever,

00:13:32.069 --> 00:13:32.079
dude."I'm

00:13:32.079 --> 00:13:33.750
telling you,

00:13:33.760 --> 00:13:35.509
there's an angel here that wants to give

00:13:35.519 --> 00:13:37.030
you a heart. Do you want the heart or

00:13:37.040 --> 00:13:39.430
not? And I told the angel, I said, "He

00:13:39.430 --> 00:13:39.440
doesn't

00:13:39.440 --> 00:13:41.110
want the heart. You hear what he

00:13:41.120 --> 00:13:43.190
just said?"And I said,

00:13:43.200 --> 00:13:44.790
"I'm out of here."And I walked away. And

00:13:44.800 --> 00:13:47.829
there's the angelic visitation. So, I go

00:13:47.839 --> 00:13:50.150
back and I get the vacuum cleaner again.

00:13:50.160 --> 00:13:52.710
And I'm just vacuuming the floors. And

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:55.269
the angel of the Lord taps me on the

00:13:55.279 --> 00:13:57.750
shoulder again. He said, "Go one more

00:13:57.760 --> 00:14:01.710
time and ask Jim if he wants this

00:14:01.710 --> 00:14:01.720
heart."I

00:14:01.720 --> 00:14:03.990
said, "You heard what he said.

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:05.670
He said he doesn't believe me."And he

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:07.269
made fun of me. I don't know

00:14:07.279 --> 00:14:08.949
what to do. He said, "Just go ask him

00:14:08.959 --> 00:14:12.629
one more time."I said, "Okay."So, I

00:14:12.639 --> 00:14:14.350
went down there and I said,

00:14:14.360 --> 00:14:16.949
"Jim, I'm coming because the

00:14:16.959 --> 00:14:19.750
angel asked me to ask you one more time.

00:14:19.760 --> 00:14:24.389
Do you want this heart?"He said, "You

00:14:24.399 --> 00:14:26.949
really do see something, don't you? You

00:14:26.959 --> 00:14:29.189
do? Like, Brandon, you really do? Like,

00:14:29.189 --> 00:14:29.199
really?"And

00:14:29.199 --> 00:14:32.230
I said, "Yeah,

00:14:32.240 --> 00:14:33.829
I'm telling you."He was standing

00:14:33.839 --> 00:14:35.189
right there. I told him I could describe what

00:14:35.199 --> 00:14:37.829
he looked like. He goes, "Well, yeah. I

00:14:37.839 --> 00:14:41.030
need healing."And I went over

00:14:41.040 --> 00:14:43.750
and I said, "In the name of Jesus, I

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:45.870
command you to be healed of this heart

00:14:45.870 --> 00:14:45.880
condition."And

00:14:45.880 --> 00:14:48.870
I watched that angel, I

00:14:48.880 --> 00:14:52.550
kid you not, drop that heart inside of

00:14:52.560 --> 00:14:54.030
Jim's

00:14:54.040 --> 00:14:56.470
chest. And I just said, "I believe you

00:14:56.480 --> 00:14:57.990
received it, brother."The angel

00:14:58.000 --> 00:15:02.509
disappeared and was gone

00:15:02.519 --> 00:15:05.430
instantaneously. Within, I don't know,

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:06.590
24—whatever,

00:15:06.600 --> 00:15:10.069
he started getting better.

00:15:10.079 --> 00:15:11.990
His heart started

00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:13.750
getting better. Now, like I said, I

00:15:13.760 --> 00:15:15.829
don't know where Jim's at now. I

00:15:15.839 --> 00:15:17.750
haven't kept in contact with

00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:20.150
these people, but I'm telling you at

00:15:20.160 --> 00:15:22.389
that moment, I believe Jim got a new

00:15:22.399 --> 00:15:25.430
heart and his flesh started getting

00:15:25.440 --> 00:15:26.990
better.

00:15:27.000 --> 00:15:29.750
Now, Jim got caught up in drugs and

00:15:29.760 --> 00:15:32.389
alcohol and things like that and he

00:15:32.399 --> 00:15:35.269
backslid really, really hard. But

00:15:35.279 --> 00:15:36.629
I don't know, like I said, I

00:15:36.639 --> 00:15:38.069
don't know where these people are, but

00:15:38.079 --> 00:15:40.230
I'm telling you at that moment, I

00:15:40.240 --> 00:15:42.790
believe with all my heart Jesus Christ

00:15:42.800 --> 00:15:45.829
gave Jim a heart and the

00:15:45.839 --> 00:15:47.670
angel brought it. So, I wanted to

00:15:47.680 --> 00:15:49.910
encourage you all about that one. But,

00:15:49.920 --> 00:15:53.069
like I said,

00:15:53.079 --> 00:15:55.829
I have so many of these

00:15:55.839 --> 00:15:58.590
visitations and

00:15:58.600 --> 00:16:00.949
manifestations and demonstrations of the

00:16:00.959 --> 00:16:03.829
glory. I've told you all about

00:16:03.839 --> 00:16:05.670
my truck. My truck's

00:16:05.680 --> 00:16:07.590
supernaturally getting pushed down the

00:16:07.600 --> 00:16:09.670
highway for two and a half miles from

00:16:09.680 --> 00:16:11.870
where I live all the way to a gas

00:16:11.880 --> 00:16:14.470
station off of one of the

00:16:14.480 --> 00:16:17.110
roads. I won't tell you

00:16:17.110 --> 00:16:17.120
because

00:16:17.120 --> 00:16:18.790
it doesn't matter what

00:16:18.800 --> 00:16:21.110
street it was, but we were pushed by an

00:16:21.120 --> 00:16:22.629
angel. And if you go back and look at

00:16:22.639 --> 00:16:25.350
that, we ran out of gas. The

00:16:25.360 --> 00:16:27.590
gas gauge was out on my truck.

00:16:27.600 --> 00:16:29.430
I forgot that I

00:16:29.440 --> 00:16:32.150
had not put gas in there where we drove

00:16:32.160 --> 00:16:34.629
to work—it was a long drive.

00:16:34.639 --> 00:16:36.629
My wife was pregnant with

00:16:36.639 --> 00:16:39.350
my daughter at the time and my other

00:16:39.360 --> 00:16:41.829
two were in the back and it was hot,

00:16:41.839 --> 00:16:44.230
probably about 97 degrees outside or

00:16:44.240 --> 00:16:46.629
more. A hot summer day. It was in the

00:16:46.639 --> 00:16:49.790
middle of July. And

00:16:49.800 --> 00:16:53.350
my truck turns off in the middle

00:16:53.360 --> 00:16:56.069
of the highway and I go over to the

00:16:56.079 --> 00:16:58.550
side. I put my hazard lights on and I

00:16:58.560 --> 00:17:01.030
told my wife,

00:17:01.040 --> 00:17:02.470
"Baby, I'm

00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:03.829
going to have to walk to the gas

00:17:03.829 --> 00:17:03.839
station."And

00:17:03.839 --> 00:17:06.150
she's big and pregnant.

00:17:06.160 --> 00:17:08.630
And I'm thinking, "This is going to

00:17:08.640 --> 00:17:11.710
be really, really

00:17:11.710 --> 00:17:11.720
bad."And

00:17:11.720 --> 00:17:14.230
I just start praying in the

00:17:14.240 --> 00:17:15.990
spirit. We're all just praying in

00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:19.110
the spirit. And lo and behold, we

00:17:19.120 --> 00:17:22.309
have this massive boom. And I think

00:17:22.319 --> 00:17:25.189
somebody has hit us, rear-ending us

00:17:25.199 --> 00:17:28.549
from behind, and our whole truck jerked

00:17:28.559 --> 00:17:31.110
and all of a sudden we started going

00:17:31.120 --> 00:17:34.470
faster and faster

00:17:34.480 --> 00:17:36.870
down the highway. I put my blinker on

00:17:36.880 --> 00:17:39.110
and I'm riding in the shoulder and I

00:17:39.120 --> 00:17:41.190
merge onto the

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:44.070
highway with the engine off. Whether you

00:17:44.080 --> 00:17:46.350
want to believe this or not, it's the

00:17:46.360 --> 00:17:48.630
truth. We're going down the highway. I'm

00:17:48.640 --> 00:17:53.430
going 70 mph with the engine off,

00:17:53.440 --> 00:17:57.510
passing people in the left-hand lane as

00:17:57.520 --> 00:17:59.270
I'm going down the highway with the

00:17:59.280 --> 00:18:00.270
truck

00:18:00.280 --> 00:18:03.990
off. That angel's pushing us all the way

00:18:04.000 --> 00:18:08.630
down through the—we exit off. We stop at

00:18:08.640 --> 00:18:11.270
the stoplight. The angel pushes us

00:18:11.280 --> 00:18:13.430
through the stoplight. Go all the way

00:18:13.440 --> 00:18:15.830
down to another stop sign and turn right.

00:18:15.830 --> 00:18:15.840
It

00:18:15.840 --> 00:18:18.070
pushes us through it, and then, yank, we

00:18:18.080 --> 00:18:20.630
get to the gas station, and it yanks the

00:18:20.630 --> 00:18:20.640
tailgate

00:18:20.640 --> 00:18:23.190
of our truck and stops us

00:18:23.200 --> 00:18:25.990
right in front of the pump. We all

00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:27.909
started screaming and praising the Lord

00:18:27.919 --> 00:18:29.990
because it was so supernatural what the

00:18:30.000 --> 00:18:32.070
Lord had just done right then. The other

00:18:32.080 --> 00:18:33.750
people at the other pumps were looking

00:18:33.760 --> 00:18:35.830
at us like, "What is going on with

00:18:35.840 --> 00:18:38.150
these people?"because we were

00:18:38.160 --> 00:18:39.430
just screaming; it was

00:18:39.440 --> 00:18:41.669
just one of those moments

00:18:41.669 --> 00:18:41.679
where

00:18:41.679 --> 00:18:43.750
you're just shaking because

00:18:43.760 --> 00:18:46.150
what's happening in the natural is

00:18:46.160 --> 00:18:48.310
coming from the supernatural and God is

00:18:48.320 --> 00:18:50.950
coming through for you again. We

00:18:50.950 --> 00:18:50.960
got

00:18:50.960 --> 00:18:53.029
pushed all the way to the gas station.

00:18:53.039 --> 00:18:54.549
I've told this story

00:18:54.559 --> 00:18:56.470
before, but it's worth telling again

00:18:56.480 --> 00:18:58.710
because it's all God and He's worthy to

00:18:58.720 --> 00:19:01.190
be praised. He's been faithful to me,

00:19:01.200 --> 00:19:03.430
and I've got to give Him

00:19:03.440 --> 00:19:05.990
the praise for it again. Then I

00:19:06.000 --> 00:19:08.710
told you all about the hospital where my

00:19:08.720 --> 00:19:11.990
wife had no pain. The angel

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:15.190
came in and laid hands on my wife

00:19:15.200 --> 00:19:17.110
during our first pregnancy. We were

00:19:17.120 --> 00:19:20.230
believing for a supernatural childbirth

00:19:20.230 --> 00:19:20.240
and

00:19:20.240 --> 00:19:23.190
no pain

00:19:23.200 --> 00:19:26.390
through childbirth. My wife was

00:19:26.400 --> 00:19:29.350
in labor with our daughter, Megan,

00:19:29.360 --> 00:19:32.710
at the time. The angel came in

00:19:32.720 --> 00:19:35.230
and laid his hands on her stomach, and

00:19:35.240 --> 00:19:39.590
up until my wife was almost

00:19:39.600 --> 00:19:42.230
completely through delivery, she felt

00:19:42.240 --> 00:19:45.669
nothing. She felt

00:19:45.669 --> 00:19:45.679
contractions—her

00:19:45.679 --> 00:19:47.350
body was

00:19:47.350 --> 00:19:47.360
contracting—but

00:19:47.360 --> 00:19:50.310
she had no pain at all.

00:19:50.320 --> 00:19:52.470
Even the doctor and the

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:54.710
people coming in—we had

00:19:54.710 --> 00:19:54.720
family

00:19:54.720 --> 00:19:56.470
trying to visit,

00:19:56.480 --> 00:19:58.070
and

00:19:58.080 --> 00:19:59.669
people go, "Why

00:19:59.679 --> 00:20:01.190
would you have people come

00:20:01.190 --> 00:20:01.200
up?"We

00:20:01.200 --> 00:20:03.510
learned our lesson. Family

00:20:03.510 --> 00:20:03.520
would

00:20:03.520 --> 00:20:06.070
try to come up and say,

00:20:06.760 --> 00:20:09.750
"That's impossible. They say you

00:20:09.760 --> 00:20:12.070
can't do that."All of a sudden, that

00:20:12.080 --> 00:20:13.669
angel took his hand. There was so much

00:20:13.679 --> 00:20:15.190
doubt and unbelief in the room. I've

00:20:15.200 --> 00:20:18.230
told you that.

00:20:18.240 --> 00:20:22.070
You get shaken by people speaking

00:20:22.070 --> 00:20:22.080
negatively

00:20:22.080 --> 00:20:24.950
around you about what God's

00:20:24.960 --> 00:20:27.190
doing. Even the doctors were saying

00:20:27.200 --> 00:20:28.870
that's impossible.

00:20:28.880 --> 00:20:30.470
The nurses, they all look at you like

00:20:30.480 --> 00:20:32.310
you're wild. They don't understand

00:20:32.320 --> 00:20:35.110
how my wife was not

00:20:35.120 --> 00:20:37.909
having any pain during childbirth, but

00:20:37.919 --> 00:20:39.909
God was doing something supernatural.

00:20:39.919 --> 00:20:42.789
This was very

00:20:42.789 --> 00:20:42.799
vital—it's

00:20:42.799 --> 00:20:45.190
very important that you

00:20:45.200 --> 00:20:48.149
learn from this. Do not let negativity

00:20:48.149 --> 00:20:48.159
into

00:20:48.159 --> 00:20:50.870
your hospital room when you

00:20:50.880 --> 00:20:54.070
are believing for a miracle because it's

00:20:54.080 --> 00:20:57.510
a robber of your faith. You

00:20:57.520 --> 00:20:59.990
hear doubt and unbelief, and just

00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:01.510
like faith cometh by hearing and hearing

00:21:01.520 --> 00:21:03.029
by the Word of God, doubt comes by

00:21:03.039 --> 00:21:04.789
hearing fear.

00:21:04.799 --> 00:21:07.350
When Jesus was

00:21:07.360 --> 00:21:08.870
raising the little girl up from the

00:21:08.880 --> 00:21:12.230
dead, He made all the other people

00:21:12.240 --> 00:21:16.230
leave the room that didn't have faith. He

00:21:16.230 --> 00:21:16.240
got them

00:21:16.240 --> 00:21:19.149
out of the

00:21:19.159 --> 00:21:22.310
house. There's a reason for that:

00:21:22.320 --> 00:21:24.310
because it robs faith. Doubt and

00:21:24.320 --> 00:21:26.549
unbelief rob you of what you're

00:21:26.559 --> 00:21:29.190
believing for. Sometimes you've got

00:21:29.200 --> 00:21:31.350
to get people out of your

00:21:31.360 --> 00:21:33.190
room. Don't let

00:21:33.200 --> 00:21:34.789
doubt out of your mouth, and don't let

00:21:34.799 --> 00:21:37.669
people in your room because they speak

00:21:37.679 --> 00:21:40.470
doubt out of their

00:21:40.470 --> 00:21:40.480
mouths.

00:21:40.480 --> 00:21:44.630
If Jesus were

00:21:44.630 --> 00:21:44.640
physically

00:21:44.640 --> 00:21:46.350
on the earth

00:21:46.360 --> 00:21:49.830
today doing miracles

00:21:49.840 --> 00:21:51.590
through us,

00:21:51.600 --> 00:21:54.149
would He tell you to leave the

00:21:54.159 --> 00:21:56.950
room? Would He tell you that

00:21:56.950 --> 00:21:56.960
you

00:21:56.960 --> 00:21:58.870
don't have faith? "Get out of

00:21:58.870 --> 00:21:58.880
here."That's

00:21:58.880 --> 00:22:00.789
what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:22:00.799 --> 00:22:02.870
You've got to be like a

00:22:02.880 --> 00:22:05.350
bulldog on a bone. You've got to

00:22:05.360 --> 00:22:07.750
believe God for your miracle and not let

00:22:07.760 --> 00:22:09.669
the devil come in through doubt and

00:22:09.679 --> 00:22:12.430
unbelief and rob you of your greatest

00:22:12.440 --> 00:22:14.630
victories. He comes in

00:22:14.630 --> 00:22:14.640
through doubt and unbelief

00:22:14.640 --> 00:22:16.149
every single time.

00:22:18.240 --> 00:22:20.149
These testimonies I'm telling you

00:22:20.149 --> 00:22:20.159
are meant

00:22:20.159 --> 00:22:22.149
to stir you up.

00:22:22.159 --> 00:22:23.510
The reason why I'm telling you all this

00:22:23.520 --> 00:22:27.669
is the Lord told me that it's time for

00:22:27.679 --> 00:22:31.070
His body to start commissioning their

00:22:31.080 --> 00:22:34.310
angels, saying, "Father, I thank You

00:22:34.320 --> 00:22:36.710
that the angels are watching over me

00:22:36.720 --> 00:22:38.950
today. They will bear me up in their

00:22:38.960 --> 00:22:40.789
hands, lest I dash my foot against the stone,"through

00:22:40.789 --> 00:22:40.799
Psalm

00:22:40.799 --> 00:22:43.029
91. I thank You

00:22:43.039 --> 00:22:45.270
that angels are watching me from the

00:22:45.280 --> 00:22:49.590
north, the south, the east, and the west.

00:22:49.600 --> 00:22:51.909
I always call in for

00:22:51.919 --> 00:22:53.590
prosperity. Father, I thank You that the

00:22:53.600 --> 00:22:55.190
angels are going from the north, the

00:22:55.200 --> 00:22:56.789
south, the east, and the west, bringing

00:22:56.799 --> 00:22:59.669
finances to me and giving me

00:22:59.679 --> 00:23:02.070
favor. We have favor in the name of

